# Cloudflare Workers/Pages 配置文件

## _routes.json
```json
{
  "routes": [
    { "pattern": "/api/*", "zone_id": null },
    { "pattern": "/*" }
  ]
}
```

## wrangler.toml (Workers)
```toml
name = "hotel-flight-price-comparison"
compatibility_date = "2024-01-01"

[env.production]
name = "hotel-flight-price-comparison-prod"

[[kv_namespaces]]
binding = "PRICE_CACHE"
id = "your-kv-namespace-id"

[[d1_databases]]
binding = "DB"
database_name = "price-comparison"
database_id = "your-d1-database-id"
```

